o pays the IELTS exam fee?","a":"In India, the student pays IDP IELTS India on ieltsidpindia.com. FLC course fee is separate."},{"q":"Can we guarantee band 7?","a":"No. We set targets from diagnostic data and track mocks — outcomes depend on student effort and attendance."},{"q":"How many mock tests?","a":"Minimum four full mocks under exam conditions; more if below target before booking."},{"q":"Retake if score is low?","a":"Booster or skill-specific sessions based on weakest band; new enrollment as per fee policy."}],"compliance":["Never guarantee an IELTS band score","Separate coaching fee from exam registration fee","Signed enrollment agreement before batch start","Record diagnostic and mock scores on client file"],"proTips":["Set target band in writing at enrollment","Review mock trends weekly — not just overall average","Confirm Academic module for every study-abroad lead","Book exam only after two mocks within 0.5 of target"],"postApproval":["Collect official TRF when released","Update client record for admissions / visa team","Celebrate success or plan retake with gap analysis"],"performance":{"ourRate":82,"industryRate":68,"stats":[{"label":"Enrollments this year","value":"214"},{"label":"Hit target band","value":"176"},{"label":"Retake / booster","value":"38"}]},"approvalFactors":[{"label":"Attendance 80%+","ours":88,"benchmark":72},{"label":"Mock completion","ours":91,"benchmark":75},{"label":"Exam-ready booking","ours":85,"benchmark":70}],"timeline":[{"weeks":"1","title":"Diagnostic, enrollment, batch & books"},{"weeks":"2–7","title":"Classes, homework, skill drills, speaking mocks"},{"weeks":"6–8","title":"Full mock tests & exam readiness review"},{"weeks":"8–10","title":"Exam booking, test day prep, score follow-up"}],"relatedServices":[{"label":"IELTS — Test reference (official test guide)","libraryId":"b2000001-0001-4000-8000-000000000071"},{"label":"IELTS Academic Crash Course","libraryId":"b2000001-0001-4000-8000-000000000073"},{"label":"IELTS Gene